{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "All schools/SEND & disability units to be fitted with CCTV",
        "additional_details": "This will give parents peace of mind, prevent potential abuse and help protect young and vulnerable children and young adults while reducing possible trauma.",
        "background": "I want the Government to make CCTV compulsory for all schools or private units with disability/SEND pupils where children are vulnerable or where there are other safeguarding concerns. It should be mandatory for the CCTV to be checked regularly  to ensure it works all the time.",
